"Leon" AKA "The Professional" was a great movie and a great start for Ms. Portman but she was only 13 then. Great cast including Jean Reno, Gary Oldman and Danny Aiello. Forget the IMDB rating of 8.6...this movie was easily a 10! Truly a classic by writer/director Luc Besson.

As far as "The Other Woman", I dunno but am willing to give it a try.
